{"tid":772720,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"就快結婚，但係 ....","createTime":"2018-08-09T03:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T06:44:21.000Z","uid":60491,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"7062a533a6903ee5806ad5397bd3ce20ee224851","tid":772720,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T03:52:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n同男朋友感情算不錯 佢對我亦好好<br />\n唔可以講性格上100%夾到<br />\n但至少大家都肯互相遷就 鬧完交好快就無事<br />\n肯坐低慢慢商量<br />\n我覺得已經好難得<br />\n但有點係有保留 就係性生活唔協調<br />\n想要個時 又話返工攰 又話太晏 想早d休息<br />\n大佬 我都有需要㗎<br />\n次次好似我迫佢 強姦佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又唔想搵sp <br />\n但呢點實在 有點「難過」<br />\n請教巴絲打們 可以點解決"},{"pid":"fd87ea8e495b991037995b94830802223bcf29a4","tid":772720,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:06:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db2b7ed0f82980ee4bf76b73c2537f754e696e68","tid":772720,"uid":71315,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"我可以屌你啊，純扑野"},{"pid":"5ffa302c19932c32c7c6d6be0b859d2670c5b3ba","tid":772720,"uid":181905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:07:32.000Z","msg":"好簡單,留低tg 我幫你解決性需要"},{"pid":"fddaf4a38ee50c5dbed5f820bfe3a1ccec9d0ab3","tid":772720,"uid":59857,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:08:46.000Z","msg":"爆菊好辛苦架 你估好撚易咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943e22b2ee959bb91f60783bd3883b0f198f9ab5","tid":772720,"uid":60491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd87ea8e495b991037995b94830802223bcf29a4","tid":772720,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:06:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:14:16.000Z","msg":"除咗呢個問題之外 佢對我好好 好錫我 <br />\n我只係想解決問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21c96472562977dc3325995193b4e976c7f4995","tid":772720,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,